translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「え、あ、そういうことが聞きたいのではなく……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Eh, ah, that's not exactly what I wanted to ask..."
"What on earth are you angry about..."
"Hmph, I don't care, I don't care!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いつまでも死んだ主人が忘れられん
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I can't forget my dead master forever.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 間抜けな馬鹿犬なぞ俺は知らん！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I don't care about any foolish stupid dog like that!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 妖怪軍団が揃ったことで、天満橋の守りは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: With the youkai army assembled, the defense of Tenmabashi,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍でも易々とは突破できぬ程、強固となった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: became so strong that even the demon army could not break through easily.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、しまった……殺してしまった……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Ah, damn... I ended up killing him..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「大丈夫、妖怪はそう簡単に死なん。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It's okay, youkai don't die so easily.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 特に黒部殿となれば尚更だ」
ダメージなど最初からなかったかのように
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: as if there was no damage from the start,
"Oh, you still want to fight? Huh?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こいつが今、人類で最強か？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Is this guy currently the strongest of humanity?"
I am the strongest in the world."
"Raging around... I feel a little better."
Do as you like with them."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 黒部は突然、ランスに背を向けた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Suddenly, Kurobe turned his back to Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あ、こら！　どこに行くつもりだ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hey, wait! Where do you think you're going!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 黒部はその姿を消した。
「あっ！　行っちまいやがった！」
恨まれてしまったのでは？」
「さっき、名前を覚えたぞ、って……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "He said he remembered your name earlier..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「けっ、何度来ても返り討ちだ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Tch, no matter how many times I come, I always get beaten back."
"More than that, if I could make him a subordinate,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 便利そうだったんだがなぁ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: he seemed like he would be useful."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「いや、ひとまずの目的は達した。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "No, for now, the goal has been achieved.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今はこれでいいだろう」
黒部という盟主を失った周囲の妖怪達は
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The youkai around who lost their leader named Kurobe

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 当初こそ戸惑っていたが、その後の
政宗の一喝により政宗を盟主として認めた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Masamune's sharp order, they acknowledged Masamune as their leader.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 黒部は空に浮かぶ月を見上げていた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kurobe was looking up at the moon floating in the sky.
